                <h3>Upload your data</h3>
                <p>Import your department spreadsheets from Raiser's Edge or any source. Fund-Raise automatically parses gift types, funds, sources, and goals — no manual data entry.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-step">
                <div class="how-step-number gold">2</div>
                <h3>See the full picture</h3>
                <p>Every department — Annual Giving, Major Gifts, Events, Direct Mail, and Legacy — on one dashboard. Compare progress, spot trends, and track against goals in real time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="how-step">
                <div class="how-step-number navy">3</div>
                <h3>Raise more, smarter</h3>
                <p>Use historical snapshots, trend analysis, and AI-powered insights to identify your strongest donors, catch at-risk relationships, and optimize campaigns before year-end.</p>
            </div>
