<!-- ═══════════════════ FAQ ═══════════════════ -->
<section id="faq" class="landing-section">
    <div class="landing-container">
        <div class="section-header">
            <div class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</div>
            <h2 class="section-heading">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    What kind of organizations is Fund-Raise built for?
                    <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Fund-Raise is purpose-built for health foundations, hospital foundations, and multi-department nonprofits that manage fundraising across distinct programs — like Annual Giving, Major Gifts, Events, Direct Mail, and Legacy Giving. If your team runs on departmental spreadsheets and reports to a board, Fund-Raise is for you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Do we need to change our existing workflow?
                    <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>No. Fund-Raise works with the spreadsheets you already produce from Raiser's Edge. Upload your existing reporting master sheets as-is — no reformatting, no new data entry. Your team keeps working the way they already do, and Fund-Raise layers intelligence on top.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    How is our data secured?
                    <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Fund-Raise uses Google OAuth for authentication — only pre-approved email addresses can access your dashboard. All data is encrypted in transit (TLS) and at rest. Your database is hosted on Render's managed PostgreSQL with automatic backups. Role-based access ensures team members only see what they need.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    Can I view historical data?
                    <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes. Every upload creates a date-stamped snapshot that's permanently stored. Use the date picker to browse any past snapshot and see exactly where your fundraising stood on any given day. This is especially useful for board reports, fiscal year comparisons, and campaign post-mortems.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    What does Fund-Raise cost?
                    <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Fund-Raise is currently available by invitation during our early access period. Contact us for pricing tailored to your foundation's size and needs. We offer flexible plans for organizations of every scale.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                    What AI features are available?
                    <svg class="faq-chevron" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M5 8l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Fund-Raise's AI tools help you identify lapsed donors at risk of churning, suggest optimal outreach timing, draft stewardship communications, and surface trends you might miss in raw data. Ask natural-language questions like "Who are my lapsed major donors?" and get instant answers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

